In solo or in relay, register now for the 11th edition of the Dinard Emerald Coast Lepape Triathlon which will take place from September 8th to 10th 2023.

You don't want to miss the opportunity to swim in the turquoise waters of the Emerald Coast, ride in the valleys of the Pays de Rance, or run in the seaside resort of Saint-Lunaire? All this under a beautiful Breton sun? No need to panic! Book your weekend from September 8 to 10, 2023 and come and challenge the triathletes and swimrunners during the 11th edition of the Dinard Côte d?Emeraude Triathlon ? Lepape.
